reviewText: I already have a region 2 version and my multi version DVD player broke. Great movie but I wish it was a region 1
Purchased Digby. WILL NOT PLAY ON MY SONY DVD PLAYER!  Waste of money!
I sure wish there was a region 1 version.
I once saw this movie as a child in England and have searched for it since but no video store has ever stocked it. So l was very excited to see it on Amazon.com.
My dog's nickname is Digby.  She is also an Old English Sheepdog.  So, this movies rocks!  (but I'm very biased!)

Great nostalgic movie from my childhood. Watching it now is funny because it is so quirky and corny but still interesting. My kids didn't get into much because it had more english humor than american, but I enjoyed it.
